        <h2>The Story of Sheikh Hamad bin Ahmad Algosaibi</h2>
        <p class="history-story-lead">The history of Ahmad Hamad Algosaibi &amp; Bros. Co. begins with Sheikh Hamad bin Ahmad Algosaibi, whose work and commercial experience laid the foundation for the family business established in the Eastern Province.</p>
        <p>From those beginnings, the Company developed into a long-standing Saudi business presence linked to the commercial and industrial growth of the Eastern Province — from early warehousing and supply roles to operating companies and investments across the Kingdom today.</p>
