<section class="section overview-section history-highlights-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head centered reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Heritage</p>
      <h2>Built Across Generations</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">Three threads run through the Group&rsquo;s story: commercial foundations in the Eastern Province, early industrial participation, and the diversified portfolio that represents the business today.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="overview-cards reveal delay-1">
      <article class="overview-card">
        <p class="overview-card-index" aria-hidden="true">01</p>
        <h3>Commercial Foundations</h3>
        <p>The Company is known for establishing the first warehouse dedicated solely to Saudi Aramco and for supplying Aramco&rsquo;s first locally purchased order for steel pipes, tugboats, and tires.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="overview-card">
        <p class="overview-card-index" aria-hidden="true">02</p>
        <h3>Industrial Participation</h3>
        <p>The Group&rsquo;s historical profile includes early industrial development in the Eastern Province, including participation in the first electric power station and the Saudi cement plant.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="overview-card">
        <p class="overview-card-index" aria-hidden="true">03</p>
        <h3>The Portfolio Today</h3>
        <p>Today the website portfolio includes 19 companies across hospitality, food, manufacturing, energy, transport, media, and travel.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

